title: TeeHee Valley (3 Remixes: 8-Bit, DS-Style, and Remastered)
description:
What better way to remaster one of my favorite video game songs than to do it three times?

Skip to around 1:35 to hear the DS-styled version of the song, and 3:10 to hear the song remastered (that's the version I think it the best)

And yes, I know that some of the notes here are shorter and have a bit of a rest compared to the original, but I, personally, like it better that way.
